Description: A simple system benchmarking & monitoring toolkit
 Guro is a powerful system monitoring and benchmarking tool that provides 
 real-time system metrics and performance tuning.
 .
 Features:
  * Real-time system metrics monitoring
  * GPU optimization (NVIDIA and AMD)
  * Performance benchmarking capabilities
  * Resource usage visualization
  * Hardware monitoring and optimization
  * Cross-platform support (Linux, Windows, macOS)